name: NEGARA HOTEL
address: Jl. Ngurah Rai No.107, Pendem, Kec. Jembrana, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82218, Indonesia
review 1: Nice and convy room. The parking area is also spacious. The room staff are friendly. Best hotel if you need to stay awhile when you want to go to Gilimanuk or from Gilimanuk.
review 2: First of all the standard room is very dark, to be honest i cannot sleep, because the room is kinda scary, i don't like dimly lit room. I'm not taking photo the room because afraid something who should not be visible will be appear if i take the photo, it sound ridiculous but this is my honest opinion. Overall the service is good, staff is very nice and helpful to me.
review 3:
Nice place at a very strategic location for transit. But make sure you call and book first. It's quite a busy hotel.
Some of the room doesn't have hot water shower and they only provide a bar of soap and towels. However, they do sell shower kit (soap, shampoo,etc) for $1.
review 4: the room is scary and dark. bad service. I ask if my room was ready, the ‚Äúreceptionist girl‚Äù didnt even look or answered me and just ask another staff through a walky talky to guide me. I can‚Äôt even charge my phone bcs there‚Äôs no electric plug in my room.
review 5: Very different with the pictures,smells bed and dirty. We was so dissapointed with this hotel. We got the different rooms from what we've booked. The breakfast lady was alone so we had to wait almost 40 minutes for the soto. Overall we can call this place as a motel rather than a hotel.

name: KFC
address: Jl. Ngurah Rai, Pendem, Kec. Negara, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82218, Indonesia
review 1: The one and only KFC outlet in Town, need to improve the quality control of the food. The portion and taste a lil bit different from the outlet in Denpasar
review 2: The only fast food choice in Jembrana. Clean place but the queue always long. The service need to be accelerated.

Very dirty and old KFC
A lot of positions from menu was out of stock.

review 5: The good place for rest area in negara city
